name: appmixer.lemonsqueezy.core.FindProducts
author: Appmixer <info@appmixer.com>
description: Retrieves a list of product objects ordered by name. You can filter products by providing a store_id.

storeId.tooltip: ID of the store to filter products.
storeId.label: Store Id

outputType.label: Output Type
outputType.tooltip: Choose whether you want to receive the result set as one complete list, or first item only or one item at a time or stream the items to a file.
